experience.detail: CognitiveScale is an AI based startup which focuses on building AI platforms and ethical AI tools. At CognitiveScale I worked on developing healthcare based products using CognitiveScaleâ€™s ethical AI technology. The internship was setup in a shark tank based format where we got split into teams and were given an industry to build products for. My team included a PHD level machine learning specialist, marketing specialist, software engineer (me), and a Healthcare specialist. We worked together to build a website backed by CognitiveScale's ethical ai software, and machine learning models using real healthcare data from the state of Delaware. Our team won the Audience award in the final competition.

I used various python tools to analyze datasets and develop models and neural networks on these datasets. Worked with regression modeling, MLP neural networks, market basket analysis and natural language processing. Used data focusing on dental insurance.
